      >
        <h2
          class="text-3xl text-honey-flower-800 font-Trebuchet font-bold text-center py-1.5"
        >
          Member Strength Trainings
        </h2>
        <p class="py-2 text-black text-2xl font-bold text-center">
          <i>Sign up via Mobilize below.</i>
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-honey-flower-800 text-xl">
              Weekend Dates
            </h3>
            <div class="text-black text-bold text-md md:text-lg text-left">
              <i>Saturdays from 10am - 2pm PST.</i>
              <div class="bg-slate-500 h-0.5 w-full my-2.5"></div>
              <p class="py-2">
                Session 1 - July 27, 2024
                <br />
                <span class="text-supernova-700"
                  >Member Strength Training Session #1: The Structured
                  Conversation and the Story of I</span
                >
                <br />
                <i class="font-bold">Thank you to all members who attended!</i>
              </p>
              <p class="py-2">
                Session 2 - September 7th, 2024
                <br />
                <span class="text-supernova-700"
                  >Member Strength Training Session #2: Assessing your
                  Workplace, Charting and List Work</span
