              <div class="flex bg-slate-500 h-[1px] w-full my-2.5 items-end">
              </div>
              <p class="py-2">
                Session 1 - August 13th to 14th, 2024
                <br />
                <span class="text-supernova-700"
                  >Member Strength Training Session #1: The Structured
                  Conversation and the Story of I</span
                >
                <br />
                <i class="font-bold">Thank you to all members who attended!</i>
              </p>
