                <br />
                <span class="text-supernova-700"
                  >Member Strength Training Session #3: AAR "Affirm, Answer,
                  Redirect"</span
                >
                <br />
                <i class="font-bold">Thank you to all members who attended!</i>
              </p>
              <p class="py-2">
                Session 4 - November 12th to 13th, 2024
